text: The Subway outlet at Oasis Terrace is a clean and modern spot to grab a quick bite. The sandwiches are fresh and flavorful, with a good selection of bread, fillings, and sauces. While the service is efficient, the seating area is cozy, making it a nice place to enjoy your meal. A great option for a healthy and satisfying choice when youâ€™re in the area!

I ordered a six-inch chicken, egg, and cheese sandwich, as well as a spicy Italian wrap. The staff were attentive, helpful, and friendly. Plenty of seating available. Good to see more choices at Oasis.

Service was great and staff was calm despite having 2 customers waiting in the queue. He was apologetic that they had to wait while serving me. Restaurant was clean and ample seats were available around 5.30pm

The outlet now able to choose/customise the usual selection. Clean and easy to find seats for now.

Good choice for late dinner. Friendly staff.

Clean outlet with plenty of tables. The music was so loud that we couldn't hear the staff speak behind their masks and I felt bad I had to keep asking them to repeat 2-3 times. Even had to talk more loudly to my friend when we were eating.
